Emissions
Due to its electric drive, there are no local emissions from G.H.O.S.T. G.H.O.S.T is 100% carbon neutral.
tCO2eq
The quantity that describes, for a given mixture and amount of greenhouse gas, the amount of CO2 that would have the same global warming potential.
